---
// ArchitectureCarousel.astro — Bento Grid case study
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-28">
  <div class="text-center mb-20">
    <p class="font-mono text-green text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">System Architecture</p>
    <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-5">Under the Hood</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">
      The architecture and intelligence layer behind the qualification engine.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Bento Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 auto-rows-auto">

    <!-- Card 1: The Problem — lg col-span-2 -->
    <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-10 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
        <div class="shrink-0 p-3 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-red-400 mt-1">
          <!-- Lucide: alert-triangle -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-3">The Partnership Triage Problem</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Early-stage FinTech companies receive dozens of inbound partner requests across scattered channels—forms, LinkedIn, cold emails.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-5">
            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-800">
              <p class="text-red-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">Founders' Gut Decisions</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Qualifications rely on manual review and intuition rather than structured, repeatable data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg p-4 border border-slate-800">
              <p class="text-red-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">Institutional Memory Leakage</p>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Good opportunities get missed. Consistent rationale is never logged. Knowledge leaves with the founder.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: The Impact — metric cards stacked -->
    <div class="col-span-1 group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-8 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-green/10 border border-green/20 text-green">
          <!-- Lucide: bar-chart-2 -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" x2="18" y1="20" y2="10"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="20" y2="4"/><line x1="6" x2="6" y1="20" y2="14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Built for Scale</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 border border-slate-800">
          <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Per Analysis</span>
          <span class="text-green font-mono font-bold text-xl">€0.003</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 border border-slate-800">
          <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Saved / Lead</span>
          <span class="text-green font-mono font-bold text-xl">25 min</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-900/60 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 border border-slate-800">
          <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">BaFin Context</span>
          <span class="text-green font-mono font-bold text-xl">100%</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: The Architecture — full CSS flow diagram -->
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-10 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-10 justify-center">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400">
          <!-- Lucide: git-branch-plus -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 3v12"/><path d="M18 9a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/><path d="M6 21a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/><path d="M15 6a9 9 0 0 1-9 9"/><path d="M18 15v6"/><path d="M21 18h-6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Hybrid Intelligence System</h3>
      </div>

      <!-- Flow Diagram -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-0 font-mono text-sm w-full">

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 px-4 py-4 text-center w-full sm:w-36 shrink-0">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Step 1</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-white">Structured<br/>Intake</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:w-10 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600">
          <span class="hidden sm:block text-2xl">→</span>
          <span class="sm:hidden text-2xl py-1">↓</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/40 px-4 py-4 text-center w-full sm:w-36 shrink-0">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Step 2 · LLM</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-blue-400">AI<br/>Analysis</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:w-10 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600">
          <span class="hidden sm:block text-2xl">→</span>
          <span class="sm:hidden text-2xl py-1">↓</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-yellow-500/40 px-4 py-4 text-center w-full sm:w-36 shrink-0">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Step 3 · n8n</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-yellow-400 break-words">Rule-Based<br/>Scoring</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sm:w-10 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600">
          <span class="hidden sm:block text-2xl">→</span>
          <span class="sm:hidden text-2xl py-1">↓</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl border border-green/40 px-4 py-4 text-center w-full sm:w-36 shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(100,255,218,0.07)]">
          <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Step 4</div>
          <div class="font-bold text-green">Decision</div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p class="text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed mt-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        AI extracts insights from unstructured input. The deterministic rule engine layers on governance based on revenue, team size &amp; regulatory context. Humans make the final call with structured intelligence—not raw text.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4: The Intelligence -->
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-10 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-400">
          <!-- Lucide: cpu -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><path d="M15 2v2"/><path d="M15 20v2"/><path d="M2 15h2"/><path d="M2 9h2"/><path d="M20 15h2"/><path d="M20 9h2"/><path d="M9 2v2"/><path d="M9 20v2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">What Makes It Work</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold font-mono">01</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-1">Segment Classification</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Automatically categorizes applications into niches (Payments, Lending, RegTech) for customized scoring weights.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold font-mono">02</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-1">Regulatory Risk Tagging</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Flags missing BaFin licenses or AML exposure, calculating a definitive risk percentile before sales engages.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green/20 text-green flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-xs font-bold font-mono">03</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-200 mb-1">The Audit Trail</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every decision is logged permanently with AI reasoning and deterministic JSON output, creating institutional memory.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 5: Philosophy mini-card -->
    <div class="col-span-1 group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-green/10 border border-green/20 text-green w-fit mb-6">
        <!-- Lucide: shield-check -->
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-3">Human-in-the-Loop</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">AI handles heavy lifting. Deterministic rules add governance. Humans make the final call. Built for compliance-sensitive markets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
